    "FedML's integration with popular machine learning frameworks like TensorFlow and PyTorch allows for seamless adaptation of foundation models in federated settings.",
    "• FederatedScope-LLM [241] is an extension of Federat-edScope focused on LLMs.",
    "It addresses the unique challenges of training LLMs in a federated environment, such as efficient communication and privacy preservation.",
    "This platform is relevant for FedFM as it provides specialized tools to manage the complexities of FedFM.",
    "• FATE-LLM [242], a specialized version of the Federated AI Technology Enabler (FATE) platform, is tailored for LLMs."
